{{!--
  Password reset email body.
  Override this partial in your project (e.g. src/views/security/passwordResetEmail.hbs) to customise copy and layout.

  Data:
  - resetUrl: full URL to the reset-password page (e.g. https://example.com/resetPassword?token=...)
  - siteName: name of the website (from website.name)
  - email: recipient email (for personalisation)
--}}
<p>Hi,</p>
<p>Someone requested a password reset{{#if email}} for {{email}}{{/if}}.</p>

<p>To choose a new password, open this link:</p>
<p><a href="{{resetUrl}}">Reset password</a></p>
<p>Or copy and paste into your browser:</p>
<p>{{resetUrl}}</p>

<p>This link expires in 1 hour. If you didn't request a reset, you can ignore this email.</p>

{{#if siteName}}
<p>— {{siteName}}</p>
{{/if}}
